# groupadd

> Add user groups to the system
> See also: groups, groupdel, groupmod
> More information: https://manned.org/groupadd

- Create a new group:

`sudo groupadd {string group}`

- Create a new system group:

`sudo groupadd --system {string group}`

- Create a new group with the specific groupid:

`sudo groupadd --gid {any something} {string group}`
